Dice
====

Dice is a minimalist Dependency Injection Container for PHP.


Installation
------------

Just require dice.php in your project and you're good to go.

For full documentation see http://r.je/dice.html


Updates
------------

28/02/2014 - Added basic namespace support. Documentation update will follow shortly.
			 Also moved the XML loader into its own file, you'll need to include it separately if you're using it.